            <title>[HBASE-1975] SingleColumnValueFilter: Add ability to match the value of previous versions of the specified column</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1975</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
